    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Code放到LedgerService，然后画一条线从Code连到Define。现在FraudDetection这边有Audit、Bail、Barg、Define四个节点，LedgerService有Code。",
