      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Risk→Signal→Barg，这条链路我加上了。还有Place和Press，这两个也是外部节点吧？我看到它们之间有关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
